data.description:
1: CryptoQuant CEO: Strategy purchases faster than BTC mining, and has achieved an annualized deflation advantage of 2.23%;
2: OTHERS market value exceeds 27.4 billion US dollars, up 20% in three days;
3: "Rich Dad Poor Dad" author: Stay away from "fake currency" and turn to BTC, gold and silver;
4: The giant whale transferred 7,665 ETH and 2.17 million ENA to Binance, and the floating loss of ETH reached 8.84 million US dollars;
5: Hosico briefly broke through 0.05 US dollars, rising more than 81% in nearly 2 hours;
6: The new version of the stablecoin bill GENIUS requires Tether to accept US jurisdiction regardless of the place of registration;
7: A whale spent about 13 million USDC to short BTC, ETH and SOL with 5x leverage;
8: A giant whale address transferred nearly 300 billion from Binance PEPE;
9: Aevo governance proposal AGP-2 has been passed and will resume the monthly on-chain repurchase plan;
10: Bitunix analyst: ETF funds are flowing in strongly, BTC rose 9.3% this week to $103,000, with short-term support at $94,200.
